{
  "texts": [
    "The entire fine-tuning process requires approximately 7 hours on 8 NVIDIA A100 GPUs.",
    "Evaluation on 3D VQAThe training datasets covers 75K scene-language instruction pairs contraining 25K 3D VQA data.",
    "We choose Vicuna-7b and LLaVA1.5-7b as our basic LLM and MLLM.",
    "We evaluate our method on ScanQA [13] validation dataset, which employs VoteNet [16] to generate object proposals, integrating them with text embeddings.",
    "BaselinesThe compared baselines contain 3 categories: supervised expert models, general 3D-LLMs with alignment and 3D-LLMs without alignment."
  ]
}